Key Match Events: Chad 0-2 Ivory Coast. The Elephants make it two wins from as many qualifiers and top Group G with six points.
Oumar Diakite strikes 10 minutes into the second half to give Ivory Coast a firm control of the game.
Jean-Philippe Krasso breaks the deadlock three minutes into injury time in the first half, leading Ivory Coast to a 1-0 lead at the break.
